<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Alerts on</title><link>https://openksc.github.io/docs/v4.1/11-use-extensions/05-observability-platform/07-whizard/05-alert-management/02-alerts/</link><description>Recent content in Alerts on</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><atom:link href="https://openksc.github.io/docs/v4.1/11-use-extensions/05-observability-platform/07-whizard/05-alert-management/02-alerts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>View Alert List</title><link>https://openksc.github.io/docs/v4.1/11-use-extensions/05-observability-platform/07-whizard/05-alert-management/02-alerts/01-view-an-alert-list/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://openksc.github.io/docs/v4.1/11-use-extensions/05-observability-platform/07-whizard/05-alert-management/02-alerts/01-view-an-alert-list/</guid><description>&lt;div class="paragraph">
&lt;p>This section describes how to view the global alert list in the Whizard Observability Center.&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="paragraph">
&lt;p>The &lt;strong>Built-in Alerts&lt;/strong> and &lt;strong>Custom Alerts&lt;/strong> pages in the Whizard Observability Center display alerts generated by the system based on global alerting rule groups, not including alerts generated by cluster and project alerting rule groups.&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="sect1">
&lt;h2 id="_prerequisites">Prerequisites&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="sectionbody">
&lt;div class="paragraph">
&lt;p>You should have the &lt;strong>platform-admin&lt;/strong> role on the KubeSphere platform. For more information, see &lt;a href="../../../../../../05-users-and-roles/01-users/">Users&lt;/a> and &lt;a href="../../../../../../05-users-and-roles/02-platform-roles/">Platform Roles&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="sect1">
&lt;h2 id="_steps">Steps&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="sectionbody">
&lt;div class="olist arabic">
&lt;ol class="arabic">
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Log in to the KubeSphere web console with a user having the &lt;strong>platform-admin&lt;/strong> role.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Click &lt;span class="image">&lt;img src="https://openksc.github.io/images/ks-qkcp/zh/icons/grid.svg" alt="grid" width="18" height="18"/>&lt;/span> in the upper-right corner of the page and click &lt;strong>Whizard Observability Center&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Click &lt;strong>Global Alerts &amp;gt; Built-in Alerts/Custom Alerts&lt;/strong> in the left navigation pane.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="exampleblock">
&lt;div class="content">
&lt;div class="ulist">
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
